Thank you 2023. 💫

Time is something we never get back. Live the life you want to live, and experience things you’ve never done before. 

With many moments of not documenting a thing this year - being present and enjoying the moment is far more real and sentimental because we are simply present with ourselves and the beauty around us. 

Try new things, meet new people, start the business you want, give random acts of kindness, tell others you appreciate them, check in with yourself, poke fun of yourself and laugh at it, never regret a thing and never settle for anything that doesn’t feel right. 

Because life is about doing what makes you happy. Sometimes there’s levels of uncertainty, and sometimes it doesn’t make sense but it will make sense when it’s suppose to make sense. #doesthatmakesense 😉

Blessed, forever grateful & wishing you a Happy New Year. 

xx Rach ♥️✨🌹
